    </button>

    <div id="result" class="result-card">
        <div class="res-box">
            <h3 id="res-title" style="margin:0 0 10px 0; color:var(--primary); font-size:18px; font-weight:800;"></h3>
            <p style="margin:6px 0; font-size:14.5px;"><strong>🍰 今日主打推荐：</strong> <span id="res-restaurant" style="color:#ff5c81; font-weight:700;"></span></p>
            <p style="font-size:12px; color:var(--text-muted); margin:6px 0 14px 0;">🌸 小提示：点击地图路线标记可以弹出翻转卡片，随意切换餐厅/景点图鉴或详情手记哦！</p>
            
            <div id="res-route"></div>
            
            <div style="font-size: 13px; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 15px; color: var(--secondary);">AMap 导航实况路线解说：</div>
            <div id="panel"></div>
            
            <button class="secondary-btn" onclick="openAMapApp()" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2b84ca, #4dafff); margin-top: 15px;">🚀 直接调起高德地图App导航</button>
            <button class="secondary-btn" onclick="generateTravelJournal()">✍️ 开启/查看专属有图手账本</button>
        </div>
        
        <div class="map-wrapper">
            <div class="layer-ctrl">
                <label><input type="checkbox" id="satellite-layer" onchange="toggleLayers()"> 🛰️ 3D卫星影像</label>
                <label><input type="checkbox" id="traffic-layer" onchange="toggleLayers()"> 🚙 实时路况</label>
            </div>
            <div id="map-container"></div>
        </div>

        <div id="journal-section" class="journal-container">
            <div class="journal-tape"></div>
            <div class="journal-paper">
                <h4 style="margin:0 0 10px 0; color:#c05c6e; font-size:16px; font-weight:800; border-bottom:2px dashed #ffcbd7; padding-bottom:4px;">🐾 咪呀广州 · 浪漫街头游记手账</h4>
                <div id="journal-auto-text" style="font-size:13.5px; color:#554235; font-weight:bold; margin-bottom:10px;"></div>
                
                <div style="font-size:13px; color:#a08070; font-weight:bold; margin-top:15px; text-decoration:underline;">✍️ 我的手写心情随笔：</div>
                <textarea id="journal-user-note" class="journal-textarea" placeholder="在这里写下你的探店心得、搞笑瞬间或避坑指南吧... (内容会自动安全保存哦) " oninput="saveJournalToStorage()"></textarea>
                
                <div style="font-size:13px; color:#a08070; font-weight:bold; margin-top:15px;">📸 我的旅途手账相册：</div>
                <div style="margin: 8px 0;">
                    <label style="background:var(--primary); color:#fff; padding:6px 14px; border-radius:12px; font-size:12px; cursor:pointer; display:inline-block; font-weight:bold;">
                        ➕ 点击上传/记录今天拍的照片
                        <input type="file" id="journal-photo-input" accept="image/*" multiple style="display:none;" onchange="handlePhotoUpload(this)">
                    </label>
                </div>
                <div id="journal-photos" class="journal-photo-grid"></div>
                
                <button class="secondary-btn" style="background:linear-gradient(135deg, #c05c6e, #ff7e9d); margin-top:20px;" onclick="clearSavedJournal()">🧹 清空当前手账记录</button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

